\pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs22 a. (133\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs22 \endash 153\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs22 ) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[1].6922/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\caps\lang1033\fs22\chcbpat17 Predigt}}\plain \f1\caps\lang1033\fs22  von {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[0].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\caps\lang1033\fs22\chcbpat17 Johannes dem Evangelisten}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs22 . \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs22 >Dise predie tet v\u180 \'b4ns brvder Hv\plain \f1\i\super\lang1033\fs24 o\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs22 go der lesemaister von Constence von dem lieben vnd dem gvten sant Johannes ewangeliste.< {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://5650[0].5666d/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs22\chcbpat17 >E<cce ewangelizo vobis gaudium magnum}}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://5650[0].5666d/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs22\chcbpat17  [Lc 2,10].}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs22  {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://5650[0].5666d/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs22\chcbpat17 >D<o nv got ellv dinch geschv}}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://5650[0].5666d/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\i\super\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 o}}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://5650[0].5666d/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs22\chcbpat17 f, do geschv}}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://5650[0].5666d/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\i\super\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 o}}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://5650[0].5666d/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs22\chcbpat17 f er ain iechlich dinch also}}\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs22 , dc ez frvht brehti nah sinem geslehte, vnd da von do wolte got mensche werden, dc er vnser menslikvn na\plain \f1\lang1033\fs22 [133\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs22 ]\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs22 tvre zvge in sine gotlikvn natvre, dc sin menslichv natvre frvht brehti nah gotlikem geslehte ...\~\endash \~... Sit nv in disem sv\plain \f1\i\super\lang1033\fs24 o\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs22 eze vnd minnechliken hailigen\plain \f1\lang1033\fs22  [153\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs22 ] \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs22 daz himelrich vnd ellv wnne beslozen waz, so mag ime got niht virzihen. Da von svn wir in biten, dc er vns irwerbe vmbe vnsern herren, dc wir niemer von ime gescheiden werden. Des helfe mir vnd iv der vater vnd der svn vnd der hailige geist. Amen.}

